# Upstash Redis Environment Variables
# Required for backend todo list persistence
# Get these values from: Upstash Console → Redis Database → REST API section

# Upstash Redis REST URL (required)
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=your_upstash_redis_rest_url_here

# Upstash Redis REST Token (required)
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=your_upstash_redis_rest_token_here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Create an Upstash Redis database at https://console.upstash.com
# 2. Copy the REST URL and Token from the database details page
# 3. Create a `.env.local` file (git-ignored) and paste the values
# 4. For production, add these to Vercel project settings → Environment Variables
#
# See docs/deployment/upstash-setup.md for detailed setup instructions
